snippet.title: Amber Heard Getting Paid For Giving Speech on Domestic Abuse | Flixet
snippet.description:
In today’s video are going to tell about Amber Heard Is Now Being Paid To Speak About Domestic Abuse. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
__________________________________________________

Amber Heard has a new gig, but it isn’t your standard Hollywood casting role and might not be something she ever intended to speak about publicly. But her recent high profile and rather disturbing run through the media because of publicized marital issues have landed Heard a public speaking job. For a price, Amber Heard will be speaking about, among other things, domestic abuse issues.
